#: src/reference/cli.md:461
msgid "`zeroclaw estop`"
msgstr "zeroclaw estop"

#: src/reference/cli.md:463
msgid "Engage, inspect, and resume emergency-stop states."
msgstr "緊急停止状態を有効化、検査、再開します。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:465
msgid ""
"Examples: - `zeroclaw estop` - `zeroclaw estop --level network-kill` - "
"`zeroclaw estop --level domain-block --domain \"*.chase.com\"` - `zeroclaw "
"estop --level tool-freeze --tool shell --tool browser` - `zeroclaw estop "
"status` - `zeroclaw estop resume --network` - `zeroclaw estop resume --"
"domain \"*.chase.com\"` - `zeroclaw estop resume --tool shell`"
msgstr ""
"例：- `zeroclaw estop` - `zeroclaw estop --level network-kill` - `zeroclaw "
"estop --level domain-block --domain \"*.chase.com\"` - `zeroclaw estop --"
"level tool-freeze --tool shell --tool browser` - `zeroclaw estop status` - "
"`zeroclaw estop resume --network` - `zeroclaw estop resume --domain \"*."
"chase.com\"` - `zeroclaw estop resume --tool shell`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:467
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw estop [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]`"
msgstr "**使用法:** `zeroclaw estop [OPTIONS] [COMMAND]`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:471
msgid "`status` — Print current estop status"
msgstr "`status` — 現在のestopステータスを表示します"

#: src/reference/cli.md:472
msgid "`resume` — Resume from an engaged estop level"
msgstr "`resume` — 有効化されたestopレベルから再開します"

#: src/reference/cli.md:476
msgid ""
"`--level <LEVEL>` — Level used when engaging estop from `zeroclaw estop`"
msgstr ""
"`--level <LEVEL>` — `zeroclaw estop`からestopを有効化するときに使用するレベル"

#: src/reference/cli.md:478
msgid ""
"Possible values: `kill-all`, `network-kill`, `domain-block`, `tool-freeze`"
msgstr "可能な値: `kill-all`、`network-kill`、`domain-block`、`tool-freeze`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:480
msgid ""
"`--domain <DOMAINS>` — Domain pattern(s) for `domain-block` (repeatable)"
msgstr ""
"`--domain <DOMAINS>` — `domain-block`用のドメインパターン（繰り返し可能）"

#: src/reference/cli.md:481
msgid "`--tool <TOOLS>` — Tool name(s) for `tool-freeze` (repeatable)"
msgstr "`--tool <TOOLS>` — `tool-freeze`用のツール名（繰り返し可能）"

#: src/reference/cli.md:485
msgid "`zeroclaw estop status`"
msgstr "zeroclaw estop status"

#: src/reference/cli.md:487
msgid "Print current estop status"
msgstr "現在のestopステータスを表示します"

#: src/reference/cli.md:489
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw estop status`"
msgstr "**使用法:** `zeroclaw estop status`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:493
msgid "`zeroclaw estop resume`"
msgstr "zeroclaw estop resume"

#: src/reference/cli.md:495
msgid "Resume from an engaged estop level"
msgstr "有効化されたestopレベルから再開します"

#: src/reference/cli.md:497
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw estop resume [OPTIONS]`"
msgstr "**使用法:** `zeroclaw estop resume [OPTIONS]`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:501
msgid "`--network` — Resume only network kill"
msgstr "`--network` — ネットワークキルのみを再開します"

#: src/reference/cli.md:502
msgid "`--domain <DOMAINS>` — Resume one or more blocked domain patterns"
msgstr ""
"`--domain <DOMAINS>` — 1つ以上のブロックされたドメインパターンを再開します"

#: src/reference/cli.md:503
msgid "`--tool <TOOLS>` — Resume one or more frozen tools"
msgstr "`--tool <TOOLS>` — 1つ以上の凍結されたツールを再開します"

#: src/reference/cli.md:504
msgid ""
"`--otp <OTP>` — OTP code. If omitted and OTP is required, a prompt is shown"
msgstr ""
"`--otp <OTP>` — OTPコード。省略されOTPが必要な場合はプロンプトが表示されます"

#: src/reference/cli.md:508
msgid "`zeroclaw cron`"
msgstr "zeroclaw cron"

#: src/reference/cli.md:510
msgid "Configure and manage scheduled tasks."
msgstr "スケジュール済みタスクを設定および管理します。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:512
msgid ""
"Schedule recurring, one-shot, or interval-based tasks using cron "
"expressions, RFC 3339 timestamps, durations, or fixed intervals."
msgstr ""
"cron式、RFC 3339タイムスタンプ、期間、または固定間隔を使用して、定期的、ワン"
"ショット、または間隔ベースのタスクをスケジュールします。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:514
msgid ""
"Cron expressions use the standard 5-field format: 'min hour day month "
"weekday'. Timezones default to UTC; override with --tz and an IANA timezone "
"name."
msgstr ""
"Cron式は標準の5フィールド形式を使用します：'分 時 日 月 曜日'。タイムゾーンの"
"デフォルトはUTCです。--tzとIANAタイムゾーン名でオーバーライドします。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:516
msgid ""
"Examples: zeroclaw cron list zeroclaw cron add '0 9 * * 1-5' 'Good morning' "
"--tz America/New_York --agent zeroclaw cron add '\\*/30 * * * _' 'Check "
"system health' --agent zeroclaw cron add '_/5 * * * \\*' 'echo ok' zeroclaw "
"cron add-at 2025-01-15T14:00:00Z 'Send reminder' --agent zeroclaw cron add-"
"every 60000 'Ping heartbeat' zeroclaw cron once 30m 'Run backup in 30 "
"minutes' --agent zeroclaw cron pause TASK_ID zeroclaw cron update TASK_ID --"
"expression '0 8 * * \\*' --tz Europe/London"
msgstr ""
"例：zeroclaw cron list zeroclaw cron add '0 9 * * 1-5' 'Good morning' --tz "
"America/New_York --agent zeroclaw cron add '\\*/30 * * * _' 'Check system "
"health' --agent zeroclaw cron add '_/5 * * * \\*' 'echo ok' zeroclaw cron "
"add-at 2025-01-15T14:00:00Z 'Send reminder' --agent zeroclaw cron add-every "
"60000 'Ping heartbeat' zeroclaw cron once 30m 'Run backup in 30 minutes' --"
"agent zeroclaw cron pause TASK_ID zeroclaw cron update TASK_ID --expression "
"'0 8 * * \\*' --tz Europe/London"

#: src/reference/cli.md:527
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw cron <COMMAND>`"
msgstr "**使用法:** `zeroclaw cron <COMMAND>`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:531
msgid "`list` — List all scheduled tasks"
msgstr "`list` — スケジュール済みのすべてのタスクをリストします"

#: src/reference/cli.md:532
msgid "`add` — Add a new scheduled task"
msgstr "`add` — 新しいスケジュール済みタスクを追加します"

#: src/reference/cli.md:533
msgid "`add-at` — Add a one-shot scheduled task at an RFC3339 timestamp"
msgstr ""
"`add-at` — RFC3339タイムスタンプでワンショットスケジュール済みタスクを追加し"
"ます"

#: src/reference/cli.md:534
msgid "`add-every` — Add a fixed-interval scheduled task"
msgstr "`add-every` — 固定間隔のスケジュール済みタスクを追加します"

#: src/reference/cli.md:535
msgid "`once` — Add a one-shot delayed task (e.g. \"30m\", \"2h\", \"1d\")"
msgstr ""
"`once` — ワンショット遅延タスクを追加します（例：\"30m\"、\"2h\"、\"1d\"）"

#: src/reference/cli.md:536
msgid "`remove` — Remove a scheduled task"
msgstr "`remove` — スケジュール済みタスクを削除します"

#: src/reference/cli.md:537
msgid "`update` — Update a scheduled task"
msgstr "`update` — スケジュール済みタスクを更新します"

#: src/reference/cli.md:538
msgid "`pause` — Pause a scheduled task"
msgstr "`pause` — スケジュール済みタスクを一時停止します"

#: src/reference/cli.md:539
msgid "`resume` — Resume a paused task"
msgstr "`resume` — 一時停止されたタスクを再開します"

#: src/reference/cli.md:543
msgid "`zeroclaw cron list`"
msgstr "zeroclaw cron list"

#: src/reference/cli.md:545
msgid "List all scheduled tasks"
msgstr "すべてのスケジュール済みタスクをリストする"

#: src/reference/cli.md:547
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw cron list`"
msgstr "**使用方法:** `zeroclaw cron list`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:551
msgid "`zeroclaw cron add`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw cron add`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:553
msgid "Add a new recurring scheduled task."
msgstr "新しい定期スケジュールタスクを追加します。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:555
msgid ""
"Uses standard 5-field cron syntax: 'min hour day month weekday'. Times are "
"evaluated in UTC by default; use --tz with an IANA timezone name to override."
msgstr ""
"標準的な5フィールドのcron構文を使用します: 'min hour day month weekday'。時刻"
"はデフォルトではUTCで評価されます。別のタイムゾーンを使用するには、IANAタイム"
"ゾーン名を指定して --tz を使用してください。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:557
msgid ""
"Examples: zeroclaw cron add '0 9 * * 1-5' 'Good morning' --tz America/"
"New_York --agent zeroclaw cron add '\\*/30 * * * _' 'Check system health' --"
"agent zeroclaw cron add '_/5 * * * \\*' 'echo ok'"
msgstr ""
"例: zeroclaw cron add '0 9 * * 1-5' 'Good morning' --tz America/New_York --"
"agent zeroclaw cron add '\\*/30 * * * _' 'Check system health' --agent "
"zeroclaw cron add '_/5 * * * \\*' 'echo ok'"

#: src/reference/cli.md:562
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw cron add [OPTIONS] <EXPRESSION> <COMMAND>`"
msgstr "**使用方法:** `zeroclaw cron add [OPTIONS] <EXPRESSION> <COMMAND>`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:564 src/reference/cli.md:589 src/reference/cli.md:613
#: src/reference/cli.md:638 src/reference/cli.md:656 src/reference/cli.md:675
#: src/reference/cli.md:695 src/reference/cli.md:707 src/reference/cli.md:760
#: src/reference/cli.md:848 src/reference/cli.md:861 src/reference/cli.md:879
#: src/reference/cli.md:899 src/reference/cli.md:928 src/reference/cli.md:964
#: src/reference/cli.md:976 src/reference/cli.md:988 src/reference/cli.md:1000
#: src/reference/cli.md:1038 src/reference/cli.md:1050
#: src/reference/cli.md:1269 src/reference/cli.md:1343
#: src/reference/cli.md:1438 src/reference/cli.md:1530
#: src/reference/cli.md:1542 src/reference/cli.md:1559
#: src/reference/cli.md:1630
msgid "**Arguments:**"
msgstr "**引数:**"

#: src/reference/cli.md:566
msgid "`<EXPRESSION>` — Cron expression"
msgstr "`<EXPRESSION>` — Cron式"

#: src/reference/cli.md:567 src/reference/cli.md:592 src/reference/cli.md:616
#: src/reference/cli.md:641
msgid "`<COMMAND>` — Command (shell) or prompt (agent) to run"
msgstr "`<COMMAND>` — 実行するコマンド(シェル)またはプロンプト(エージェント)"

#: src/reference/cli.md:571
msgid "`--tz <TZ>` — Optional IANA timezone (e.g. America/Los_Angeles)"
msgstr "`--tz <TZ>` — オプションのIANAタイムゾーン(例: America/Los_Angeles)"

#: src/reference/cli.md:572 src/reference/cli.md:596 src/reference/cli.md:620
#: src/reference/cli.md:645
msgid ""
"`--agent` — Treat the argument as an agent prompt instead of a shell command"
msgstr ""
"`--agent` — 引数をシェルコマンドの代わりにエージェントプロンプトとして扱う"

#: src/reference/cli.md:573 src/reference/cli.md:597 src/reference/cli.md:621
#: src/reference/cli.md:646
msgid ""
"`--allowed-tool <ALLOWED_TOOLS>` — Restrict agent cron jobs to the specified "
"tool names (repeatable, agent-only)"
msgstr ""
"`--allowed-tool <ALLOWED_TOOLS>` — エージェントcronジョブを指定されたツール名"
"に制限します(繰り返し可能、エージェントのみ)"

#: src/reference/cli.md:577
msgid "`zeroclaw cron add-at`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw cron add-at`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:579
msgid "Add a one-shot task that fires at a specific UTC timestamp."
msgstr "特定のUTCタイムスタンプで発火するワンショットタスクを追加します。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:581
msgid "The timestamp must be in RFC 3339 format (e.g. 2025-01-15T14:00:00Z)."
msgstr ""
"タイムスタンプはRFC 3339形式である必要があります(例: 2025-01-15T14:00:00Z)。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:583
msgid ""
"Examples: zeroclaw cron add-at 2025-01-15T14:00:00Z 'Send reminder' zeroclaw "
"cron add-at 2025-12-31T23:59:00Z 'Happy New Year!'"
msgstr ""
"例: zeroclaw cron add-at 2025-01-15T14:00:00Z 'Send reminder' zeroclaw cron "
"add-at 2025-12-31T23:59:00Z 'Happy New Year!'"

#: src/reference/cli.md:587
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw cron add-at [OPTIONS] <AT> <COMMAND>`"
msgstr "**使用方法:** `zeroclaw cron add-at [OPTIONS] <AT> <COMMAND>`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:591
msgid "`<AT>` — One-shot timestamp in RFC3339 format"
msgstr "`<AT>` — RFC3339形式のワンショットタイムスタンプ"

#: src/reference/cli.md:601
msgid "`zeroclaw cron add-every`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw cron add-every`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:603
msgid "Add a task that repeats at a fixed interval."
msgstr "固定間隔で繰り返されるタスクを追加します。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:605
msgid "Interval is specified in milliseconds. For example, 60000 = 1 minute."
msgstr "間隔はミリ秒で指定されます。例えば、60000 = 1分です。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:607
msgid ""
"Examples: zeroclaw cron add-every 60000 'Ping heartbeat'     # every minute "
"zeroclaw cron add-every 3600000 'Hourly report'    # every hour"
msgstr ""
"例: zeroclaw cron add-every 60000 'Ping heartbeat'     # 毎分 zeroclaw cron "
"add-every 3600000 'Hourly report'    # 毎時間"

#: src/reference/cli.md:611
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw cron add-every [OPTIONS] <EVERY_MS> <COMMAND>`"
msgstr "**使用方法:** `zeroclaw cron add-every [OPTIONS] <EVERY_MS> <COMMAND>`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:615
msgid "`<EVERY_MS>` — Interval in milliseconds"
msgstr "`<EVERY_MS>` — ミリ秒単位の間隔"

#: src/reference/cli.md:625
msgid "`zeroclaw cron once`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw cron once`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:627
msgid "Add a one-shot task that fires after a delay from now."
msgstr "今からの遅延後に発火するワンショットタスクを追加します。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:629
msgid ""
"Accepts human-readable durations: s (seconds), m (minutes), h (hours), d "
"(days)."
msgstr "人間が読める期間を受け入れます: s(秒)、m(分)、h(時間)、d(日)。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:631
msgid ""
"Examples: zeroclaw cron once 30m 'Run backup in 30 minutes' zeroclaw cron "
"once 2h 'Follow up on deployment' zeroclaw cron once 1d 'Daily check'"
msgstr ""
"例: zeroclaw cron once 30m 'Run backup in 30 minutes' zeroclaw cron once 2h "
"'Follow up on deployment' zeroclaw cron once 1d 'Daily check'"

#: src/reference/cli.md:636
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw cron once [OPTIONS] <DELAY> <COMMAND>`"
msgstr "**使用方法:** `zeroclaw cron once [OPTIONS] <DELAY> <COMMAND>`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:640
msgid "`<DELAY>` — Delay duration"
msgstr "`<DELAY>` — 遅延期間"

#: src/reference/cli.md:650
msgid "`zeroclaw cron remove`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw cron remove`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:652
msgid "Remove a scheduled task"
msgstr "スケジュール済みタスクを削除します"

#: src/reference/cli.md:654
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw cron remove <ID>`"
msgstr "**使用方法:** `zeroclaw cron remove <ID>`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:658 src/reference/cli.md:677 src/reference/cli.md:697
#: src/reference/cli.md:709
msgid "`<ID>` — Task ID"
msgstr "`<ID>` — タスクID"

#: src/reference/cli.md:662
msgid "`zeroclaw cron update`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw cron update`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:664
msgid "Update one or more fields of an existing scheduled task."
msgstr "既存のスケジュール済みタスクの1つ以上のフィールドを更新します。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:666
msgid "Only the fields you specify are changed; others remain unchanged."
msgstr "指定したフィールドのみが変更されます。その他は変わりません。"

#: src/reference/cli.md:668
msgid ""
"Examples: zeroclaw cron update TASK_ID --expression '0 8 * * \\*' zeroclaw "
"cron update TASK_ID --tz Europe/London --name 'Morning check' zeroclaw cron "
"update TASK_ID --command 'Updated message'"
msgstr ""
"例: zeroclaw cron update TASK_ID --expression '0 8 * * \\*' zeroclaw cron "
"update TASK_ID --tz Europe/London --name 'Morning check' zeroclaw cron "
"update TASK_ID --command 'Updated message'"

#: src/reference/cli.md:673
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw cron update [OPTIONS] <ID>`"
msgstr "**使用方法:** `zeroclaw cron update [OPTIONS] <ID>`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:681
msgid "`--expression <EXPRESSION>` — New cron expression"
msgstr "`--expression <EXPRESSION>` — 新しいcron式"

#: src/reference/cli.md:682
msgid "`--tz <TZ>` — New IANA timezone"
msgstr "`--tz <TZ>` — 新しいIANAタイムゾーン"

#: src/reference/cli.md:683
msgid "`--command <COMMAND>` — New command to run"
msgstr "`--command <COMMAND>` — 実行する新しいコマンド"

#: src/reference/cli.md:684
msgid "`--name <NAME>` — New job name"
msgstr "`--name <NAME>` — 新しいジョブ名"

#: src/reference/cli.md:685
msgid ""
"`--allowed-tool <ALLOWED_TOOLS>` — Replace the agent job allowlist with the "
"specified tool names (repeatable)"
msgstr ""
"`--allowed-tool <ALLOWED_TOOLS>` — エージェントジョブの許可リストを指定された"
"ツール名に置き換えます(繰り返し可能)"

#: src/reference/cli.md:689
msgid "`zeroclaw cron pause`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw cron pause`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:691
msgid "Pause a scheduled task"
msgstr "スケジュール済みタスクを一時停止します"

#: src/reference/cli.md:693
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw cron pause <ID>`"
msgstr "**使用方法:** `zeroclaw cron pause <ID>`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:701
msgid "`zeroclaw cron resume`"
msgstr "`zeroclaw cron resume`"

#: src/reference/cli.md:703
msgid "Resume a paused task"
msgstr "一時停止されたタスクを再開します"

#: src/reference/cli.md:705
msgid "**Usage:** `zeroclaw cron resume <ID>`"
msgstr "**使用方法:** `zeroclaw cron resume <ID>`"

