msgstr "5. CLI とコンフィグ"

#: src/hardware/hardware-peripherals-design.md:138
msgid ""
"See the [CLI reference](../reference/cli.md) for `zeroclaw hardware` / "
"`zeroclaw peripheral` subcommands and the [Config reference](../reference/"
"config.md) for the `[peripherals]` and `[[peripherals.boards]]` fields."
msgstr ""
"[CLI リファレンス](../reference/cli.md)の `zeroclaw hardware` / `zeroclaw "
